OL,5,G2355 I Was A Teenage Sex Pistol
OL,6,     FA founding Sex Pistol reveals the
OL,7,     Fband's chaotic rise, from London's
OL,8,     Fgrim 1970s streets to global
OL,9,     Fnotoriety. Sharing untold stories
OL,10,     Fof punk's birth and bandmate
OL,11,     Fdynamics.
OL,12,G0140 The Public Image Is Rotten
OL,13,     FAfter the breakup of the Sex
OL,14,     FPistols, John Lydon and John
OL,15,     FRotten formed Public Image Ltd. A
OL,16,     Fnever-before-seen look at one of
OL,17,     Fmusic's most influential and
OL,18,     Fcontroversial careers.
